Returns the last and all the rest of the elements of the slice, or `None` if it is empty.

# Examples

```
let x = &[0, 1, 2];

if let Some((last, elements)) = x.split_last() {
    assert_eq!(last, &2);
    assert_eq!(elements, &[0, 1]);
}
```
